OL,3,CFormer teacher from South
OL,4,CGloucestershire charged with historic
OL,5,Csex offences
OL,7,FA former teacher from South
OL,8,FGloucestershire has been charged with
OL,9,Fhistoric sexual offences against boys.
OL,11,FFavid Henry Shelly Wright, 79, is due
OL,12,Fbefore Bristol Magistrates Court on
OL,13,FThursday (May 21) accused of 11
OL,14,Foffences.
OL,16,FThe charges relate to offences
OL,17,Fallegedy committed in the 1980s and
OL,18,F1990s at Queen Elizabeth's Hospital
OL,19,FIndependent School in Bristol.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
