CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1779304271
OL,3,CFormer teacher from South
OL,4,CGloucestershire charged with historic
OL,5,Csex offences
OL,7,FMr Wright, of Longwell Green, worked
OL,8,Fat the school as a teacher and
OL,9,Fboarding master, and later as a non-
OL,10,Fteaching member of staff.
OL,12,FThe school has released a statement
OL,13,Fsaying: "We are aware of this matter
OL,14,Fand have been co-operating with the
OL,15,Fpolice throughout the course of their
OL,16,Finvestigation."
OL,18,FPolice say the charges follow an
OL,19,Finvestigation which begun in 2020.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
