CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1779304271
OL,3,CFormer teacher from South
OL,4,CGloucestershire charged with historic
OL,5,Csex offences
OL,7,FDetective Inspector Hannah Marsh said
OL,8,F"Our inquiries have resulted in the
OL,9,Fdefendant being charged with 11
OL,10,Foffences against five boys.
OL,12,F"We're keeping the victims updated on
OL,13,Fthe progress of this investigation and
OL,14,Fwill continue to provide them access
OL,15,Fto any specialist support or advice
OL,16,Fthey need."
